  "title": "💥EVENTS & MARKETING 🤝🏻- WORK AT FUN EVENTS🧑🏻‍🚀 & EARN UP ⬆️ TO $4000 A MTH🤑 [ NO EXP NEEDED👶]",
  "description": "<p><strong>THIS IS NOT YOUR TYPICAL 9–6</strong> 🥱<br />But a sales & marketing job that provides training too, so no experience needed.</p><p>We’re building a young events team for major brand campaigns. No cold calls. Just real people, real crowds, real experience.</p><p>‼️ <strong>WHAT YOU’LL ACTUALLY DO</strong><br />• Represent well-known brands across SG<br />• Work on your feet, not from a chair<br />• Learn how to communicate & lead a team</p><p>‼️ <strong>YOU’LL FIT RIGHT IN IF</strong><br />• You enjoy talking to people (or want to get better at it)<br />• You like fast-paced environments<br />• You learn best by doing, not watching<br />• You want a fun working environment <br /><br /><strong>‼️WHAT’S IN IT FOR YOU</strong><br />• Structured growth<br />• multiple workshops provided <br />• A driven, supportive team culture<br />• Opportunities to travel & work across regions</p>",
